Combine the arrowroot (or cornstarch), SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and water in a medium saucepan, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and cornstarch dissolve. Stir in cranberries and diced orange. Bring mixture to a boil, stirring often, over medium-high heat; reduce heat, and simmer, stirring often, 5 minutes or until cranberry skins begin to pop and mixture begins to thicken. Set aside to cool. Cover and chill at least 3 hours. Serve cold or warm over your favorite roasted meats.